Sheikh Hamdan Bin Mohammed Bin Rashid Al Maktoum, Crown Prince of Dubai and Chairman of Dubai Executive Council, sends a New Year’s Day greetings message to the Government of Dubai employees on Jan.1, 2022. The Crown Prince of Dubai expressed his utmost pride in every one of the employees for being companions and partners in Dubai. The message reads, “To my devoted Dubai Government team, New Year Tragedy: Stampede At India Religious Shrine Kills 12 Turkey Raises Prices Of Electricity, Natural Gas In New Year Greetings to you. Today, I’m writing this letter to express my utmost pride in every one of you for being companions and partners in Dubai, remarkable journey of success. It has been 50 years since the formation of the union, and within those five decades, we have achieved milestones that no other nation was able to accomplish before. The success that the UAE and Dubai have witnessed was only possible because of your devotion, dedication and relentless determination. You have certainly lived up to the lessons echoed by His Highness Sheikh Mohammed Bin Rashid Al Maktoum, who taught us to only aim for first place and nothing less. “As we welcome the year 2022, let us challenge ourselves and unite our efforts to push forward and drive Dubai to new heights. Your eagerness and perseverance are the cornerstone of our success. Simply put, Dubai’s prosperity lies within your hands. It is because of you the Government of Dubai continues to excel and pioneer to best serve our people, citizens and residents. “Happy new year to you and your loved one. Yours sincerely, “Hamdan Bin Mohammed Bin Rashid Al Maktoum.”